name: Moon in Her Eyes
description: This is a self portrait I took one night just before I went partying.  The theme of the night was "Weinmar" and the party was said to be both elegant and debaucherous, with a fetish undertone and a very permissive environment full of raunchy live shows.  It was a few weeks after I'd moved to Berlin and a few weeks before the first Corona lockdown.  I had no idea what was coming... I made this dress and moon headdress a couple days before I snapped this image.
